Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.60,0:00:11.97,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,猛烈的雨令心頭震動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.67,0:00:16.04,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,像那日一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.35,0:00:23.41,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,直至昨日我一直\N追逐着的夢想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.79,0:00:27.59,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,我現在仍然相信它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.46,0:00:34.22,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,沒終結的防衛也不要緊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.30,0:00:42.26,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,只要你繼續凝望着我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.67,0:00:45.20,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,STAND UP TO THE VlCTORY
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.64,0:00:48.70,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,迎接過不知多少個早晨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.44,0:00:53.44,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,將來一定會抓緊給你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.75,0:00:56.27,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,STAND UP TO THE VlCTORY
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.79,0:00:58.45,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,因為在那對面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.79,0:01:05.59,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,即使甚麽也沒有都不要緊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.16,0:01:14.63,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,只要懷着沒人能代替你的笑臉

Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.15,0:01:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在俘虜收容所\N舉行婚禮是為了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.75,0:01:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,令監視的士兵疏忽的作戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.19,0:01:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為馬其杜利亞受到空襲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.86,0:01:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連賀斯Jr的\N船員成功逃脫了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.26,0:01:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是， 胡索被使用\N艾勒度的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.27,0:01:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,機動戰士捉住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.34,0:01:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新的機動戰士V2
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.81,0:02:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去奪回機動戰士的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.45,0:02:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還未回來嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.75,0:02:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就回來了， 要堅守下去！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.79,0:02:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡索還未回來嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.56,0:02:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抵抗真是頑強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.59,0:02:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用連你們也開鎗吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.36,0:02:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想開鎗也沒子彈啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.40,0:02:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奧迪羅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.93,0:02:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連素芝你也幫手！停止呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.48,0:02:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是在廣場陳列的\N機動戰士呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.28,0:02:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我軍的機動戰士\N在做甚麽呀！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.39,0:02:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡索的V高達不在嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.49,0:02:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奧利華， 瑪貝德，\N由加和歌莉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.42,0:02:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用對機動戰士\N大砲是不行的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.89,0:02:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,認真的嗎！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.16,0:02:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡進行機動戰士戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.37,0:02:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而引擎爆炸的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.67,0:02:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,港口會被炸成粉碎的  ！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.77,0:02:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要使用大砲！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.47,0:02:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要令機動戰士爆炸呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.34,0:03:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙港口在這個\N殖民衛星的中心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.91,0:03:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在連接宇宙港口的\N一個區域内
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.41,0:03:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡索被卑斯柏的\N機動戰士捉住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.49,0:03:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡迪珍娜小姐在裡面吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.45,0:03:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.82,0:03:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,核戰機被捉住時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.46,0:03:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我聼到你的呼吸聲！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.23,0:03:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而你猶疑我就已經知道了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.43,0:03:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡迪珍娜小姐！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.23,0:03:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你為何要駕駛機動戰士！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.97,0:03:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.33,0:03:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請你就地殺死我吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.34,0:03:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我講過你太多說話啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.81,0:03:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要想逃走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.28,0:03:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使是小孩， 但或許能成為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.35,0:03:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,親類型人的話，\N我不會大意的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.85,0:03:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不會放你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.45,0:03:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是個比純子小姐更強的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.86,0:03:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,露比 . 施羅上尉， 交給你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.76,0:03:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無錯 ， 處理這種事\N我比你更純熟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.40,0:03:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全體人員等候命令！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.33,0:03:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫機動戰士集合在甲板！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.37,0:04:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.50,0:04:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡索怎樣了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.67,0:04:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瑪貝德小姐！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.24,0:04:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他立即會回來的了， 沒事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.71,0:04:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.01,0:04:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你才是他們的目標啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.78,0:04:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.45,0:04:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,破開正面的牆壁！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.48,0:04:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把能量送去主砲！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.86,0:04:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚麽！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.97,0:04:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我來遲了一步了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.64,0:04:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,俘虜逃走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.07,0:04:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連搶到手的戰艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.71,0:04:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在裝備後也給他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.54,0:04:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎樣向贊斯卡羅\N本國解釋呀？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.71,0:04:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒有你們的突襲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.95,0:04:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根本就不會發生這種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.35,0:04:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要開玩笑！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.65,0:04:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為你說這裡\N沒有連賀斯號和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.99,0:04:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷加 . 美利迪亞的機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.53,0:04:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而格諾古司令不大相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.46,0:05:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以說命令我們來偵察
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.93,0:05:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來到後， 雷加 .\N美利迪亞在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.10,0:05:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們因而動搖和慌張
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.57,0:05:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,於是才會破壞你們的設施
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.47,0:05:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了，\N連賀斯號根本就沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.64,0:05:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,進入我們的殖民衛星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.35,0:05:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你搞錯嗎！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.81,0:05:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也沒有俘虜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.58,0:05:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.32,0:05:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.42,0:05:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今後由我處置那小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.76,0:05:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,交給你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.12,0:05:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去監視機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.59,0:05:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.79,0:05:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要讓馬其杜利亞的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.56,0:05:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,碰艾勒度和基拉夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.60,0:05:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.80,0:05:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然你也是白色\N傢伙的機師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.81,0:05:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你會讓我好好享受吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.68,0:05:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你錯了吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.55,0:05:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這小孩是個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.95,0:05:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會成為我們的寶物的機師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.78,0:05:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把你放入浴缸   浴缸！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.62,0:05:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,浴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.52,0:06:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,起來！要用水浸死你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.59,0:06:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為那位小姐很可怕的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.68,0:06:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.48,0:06:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為找不到檢查用的機械人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.89,0:06:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以不能潛入殖民衛星内
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.19,0:06:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麽莎蒂所講的\N豈不是做不到？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.62,0:06:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戒備很嚴密吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.96,0:06:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無可能啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.63,0:06:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蠢材！畏首畏尾\N能做到甚麽呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.70,0:06:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰也不用去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.57,0:06:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈羅和布蘭達斯去就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.14,0:06:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.90,0:06:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈羅和布蘭達斯呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.77,0:06:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去找胡索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.12,0:07:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了， 哈羅， 布蘭達斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.90,0:07:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打算怎樣處置我呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.67,0:07:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你做甚麽！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.23,0:07:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒做甚麽吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.54,0:07:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你是新類型人的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.11,0:07:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想你\N成為同伴啊   同伴！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.54,0:07:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.04,0:07:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你這年紀\N能操縱白色傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.01,0:07:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想你讓我測試\N你的才能和適性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.75,0:07:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.62,0:07:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看過你的戰績後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.15,0:07:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能到你是個新類型人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.92,0:07:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或擁有不尋常能力的人類吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.73,0:07:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想接受我們的測試了嗎！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.63,0:07:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…  我是個普通的小孩…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.73,0:07:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想我聼你講的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.87,0:07:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就照我說話做！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.74,0:08:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難得我好好對你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.68,0:08:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停手！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.78,0:08:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會停手嗎！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.78,0:08:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.62,0:08:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然你道歉，\N你就和我合作吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.75,0:08:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你… ！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.19,0:08:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,露比 . 施羅上尉… ！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.69,0:08:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿我的衫來！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.89,0:08:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知…  知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.76,0:08:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.30,0:08:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你逃不掉的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.73,0:08:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上尉！你的衫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.70,0:08:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要來！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.74,0:08:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使少年逃脫了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.71,0:08:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也會等露比 . 施羅上尉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.98,0:08:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道， 我會去通傳的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.62,0:08:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓他逃脫的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.29,0:08:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那小孩應該會\N逃去莎蒂那裡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.16,0:08:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下來！你想穿回這個吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.20,0:08:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使我知道這樣很失禮…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.23,0:08:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是核戰機！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.04,0:09:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那樣！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.94,0:09:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在布蘭達斯和哈羅！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.05,0:09:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你… ！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.82,0:09:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能放出甚麽嗎？哈羅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.75,0:09:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別動！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.56,0:09:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,機動戰士呀！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.16,0:09:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是甚麽！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.23,0:09:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是映像啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.20,0:09:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來！哈羅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.84,0:09:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,逃脫了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.84,0:09:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不應該讓他走的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.37,0:09:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也不是比他走了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.78,0:09:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胸口怎麽了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.21,0:09:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被他咬了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.68,0:09:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基拉夫出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.95,0:09:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那位小姐很快手吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.79,0:09:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們也出發！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.80,0:10:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子…   又在成長嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.14,0:10:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看不到， 他們在追來嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.78,0:10:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.78,0:10:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是甚麽？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.31,0:10:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚麽那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.21,0:10:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚麽也沒有吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.65,0:10:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空氣在洩漏！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.70,0:10:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.17,0:10:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為甚麽？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.07,0:10:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從這裡會洩漏空氣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.40,0:10:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.94,0:10:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚麽？哪裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.24,0:10:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也忍耐一下啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.71,0:10:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是迫不得已的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.68,0:10:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不塞住我們會死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.66,0:11:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說看到尾部射器的光！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.96,0:11:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它正遠離本艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.80,0:11:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡索可能有事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.33,0:11:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多數…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.97,0:11:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,追來的機影變成三架！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.70,0:11:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我們卻不能出擊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.28,0:11:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是胡索的核戰機的求救訊號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.15,0:11:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果馬其杜利亞軍和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.92,0:11:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卑斯柏行動的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.18,0:11:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連賀斯號也只有出擊了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.09,0:11:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全體人員準備出擊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.92,0:11:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.85,0:11:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今次很麻煩啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.26,0:11:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要太深入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.72,0:11:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.86,0:11:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是哈羅發出的求救訊號吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.90,0:11:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈羅獨自是不\N能出到宇宙的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.77,0:11:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即是說它和胡索在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.47,0:11:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舒勒隊出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.30,0:11:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家要有心理準備成為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.04,0:11:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們離開殖民\N衛星的魚餌！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.51,0:11:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好！清理甲板後出發 ！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.88,0:12:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瑪貝德竟然被殖民衛星的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.45,0:12:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,離心力抛出去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.02,0:12:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歌莉， 出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.36,0:12:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不見了！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.93,0:12:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟住就會被發現啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.13,0:12:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈羅， 對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.90,0:12:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連賀斯Jr在哪裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.76,0:12:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在馬其杜利亞殖民衛星周圍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.99,0:12:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,探測到有米諾基粒子？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.39,0:12:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要出動嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.96,0:12:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然還未能確定\N是連賀斯Jr
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.80,0:12:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但如果有司令的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.17,0:12:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們可以出動的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.50,0:12:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不， 我不想再和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.20,0:12:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬其杜利亞發生事端
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.01,0:13:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連亞捷斯也來了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.58,0:13:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,令我丟臉的小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.94,0:13:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被那位小姐捉到就麻煩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.98,0:13:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為要由我來懲罰他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.09,0:13:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,露比 . 施羅上尉， 不行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.85,0:13:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要引出連賀斯Jr\N後才能攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.02,0:13:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這會令核戰機逃脫\N變得沒意思的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.43,0:13:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能逃脫嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.03,0:13:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走開！布蘭達斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.44,0:13:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的眼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.20,0:13:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無理由會看不清上楚吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.54,0:13:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是長距離米加粒子砲！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.41,0:13:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是戰艦嗎！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.18,0:13:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從連賀斯的方向來的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.42,0:13:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是甚麽！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.86,0:13:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是援軍來了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.09,0:13:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是瑪貝德小姐她們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.10,0:13:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,逃呀， 胡索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.36,0:13:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連賀斯Jr開始行動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.37,0:14:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由我來做你的對手！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.98,0:14:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又來阻住我！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.64,0:14:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瑪貝德， 歌莉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.08,0:14:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們以一對一方式戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.98,0:14:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第二戰鬥小隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.52,0:14:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去牽制馬其杜利亞軍的增援
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.35,0:14:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是白色方舟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.12,0:14:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡索， 我們是來救你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.92,0:14:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是白色方舟？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.96,0:14:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,載着V高達…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.53,0:14:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請靠近那架小型機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.60,0:14:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你指核戰機吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.13,0:14:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.57,0:14:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看前面！是哈羅呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.54,0:14:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起， 請你也收回那個球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.41,0:14:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在左面嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.41,0:14:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用左舷的閘門   知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.92,0:14:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然是哈羅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.12,0:14:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,湯馬殊嗎…  胡索…\NSOS…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.69,0:14:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.16,0:14:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們會收容他的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.19,0:14:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是…嗎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.36,0:15:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那車胎！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.00,0:15:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡索！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.20,0:15:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡索！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.64,0:15:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.01,0:15:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,湯馬殊， 我沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.11,0:15:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你裸體的嗎！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.18,0:15:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是不是V高達呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.08,0:15:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但白色方舟是沒有機艙的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.18,0:15:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡索你的飛機不能進入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.55,0:15:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫哈羅放出肥皂泡就可以吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.22,0:15:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肥皂泡！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.29,0:15:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那架小型艇！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.36,0:15:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.66,0:15:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白色方舟， 收容了胡索後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.70,0:15:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就去和連賀斯Jr會合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.57,0:15:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要在宇宙使用車胎呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.71,0:15:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以這部裝有車胎的機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.21,0:15:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也能和V高達決一高下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.05,0:15:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連那個露比 . 施羅和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.95,0:15:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷加 . 美利迪亞的\N人我也能收拾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.12,0:16:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當肥皂泡去到你那邊時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.16,0:16:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就用刀刺穿它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.23,0:16:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道， 胡索來到這裡後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.63,0:16:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就可以開門呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.30,0:16:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瑪露天娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.53,0:16:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫艦橋把空氣輸來這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.47,0:16:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.13,0:16:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡索打開機艙蓋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.54,0:16:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他裸體的嗎！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.14,0:16:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關門！瑪露天娜！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.25,0:16:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡索！布蘭達斯！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.28,0:16:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,振作呀！胡索！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.65,0:16:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,布蘭達斯！走開！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.35,0:16:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起！請你\N解開他的手扣！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.32,0:16:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡索裸體呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.46,0:16:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這當然叫裸體吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.69,0:16:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是他的…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.03,0:16:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的攻擊這麽鬆散是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.10,0:16:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為要等連賀斯Jr來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.14,0:16:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的身體沒事吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.77,0:16:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.51,0:16:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真羞家， 沒理由\N一起看着我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.21,0:16:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要借用新的機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.75,0:17:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是V高達二號嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.66,0:17:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,控制方面完全一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.09,0:17:12.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關上機艙門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.76,0:17:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,收容駕駛艙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.40,0:17:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聲音輸入密碼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.13,0:17:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.33,0:17:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要出發就快點出發啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.73,0:17:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們想前進得快一點呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.47,0:17:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是！對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.04,0:17:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是長期以來\N幫助我的核戰機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.74,0:17:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還要借助你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.55,0:17:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能觀察到離開馬其杜利亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.59,0:17:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,殖民衛星的光了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.52,0:17:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是連賀斯Jr
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.26,0:17:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,司令！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.23,0:17:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好！去捉住它！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.49,0:17:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開動主引擎！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.77,0:18:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些光！是新力軍嗎！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.58,0:18:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚麽！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.62,0:18:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是… ！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.69,0:18:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,露比 . 施羅上尉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.36,0:18:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瑪貝德小姐，\N我來遲了， 對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.66,0:18:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡索！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.13,0:18:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要使用新高達！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.10,0:18:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡迪珍娜小姐！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.37,0:18:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請你不要再來到我面前了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.70,0:18:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果那是胡索…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.12,0:18:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是戰艦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.49,0:18:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我不知道有那種戰艦啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.59,0:18:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連賀斯Jr來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.19,0:18:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚麽！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.66,0:18:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.19,0:18:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這部連名字\N也沒有的白色傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.90,0:19:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有憎恨的心\N會殺死自己啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.87,0:19:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,核戰機後面有人！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.35,0:19:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無可能的！ ！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.82,0:19:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,降低高度！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.66,0:19:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要被捲入爆炸中！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.48,0:19:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無錯， 莎蒂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.52,0:19:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很尷尬呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.39,0:19:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是說笑呀，\N我嚇了一下跳呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.79,0:19:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,使用方法不錯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.82,0:19:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.33,0:20:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但因為湯馬殊他們\N帶來白色方舟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.43,0:20:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡索才會得救啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.57,0:20:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們也是被白色方舟救起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.63,0:20:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才能救到胡索的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.50,0:20:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麽， 艾尼斯號\N已到達月球呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.81,0:20:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.51,0:20:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有甚麽事？胡索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.94,0:20:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是關於戰場擊落敵機的事嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.38,0:20:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.28,0:20:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有甚麽事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.82,0:20:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把這部…V高達\N二號的設計圖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.55,0:20:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從地球運去月球的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.49,0:20:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫做苗娜 . 米棋吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.93,0:20:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個人是我媽媽啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.76,0:20:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起隱瞞我父母的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.36,0:20:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很過份吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.93,0:20:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,苗娜 . 米棋…\N是胡索的媽媽！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.37,0:20:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已向他解釋過的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.34,0:20:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但雷加 . 美利迪亞\N成員的私事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.38,0:20:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家也是不知道的這一層
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.31,0:20:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他不明白啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.52,0:20:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,漢格魯 . 艾賓和苗娜 . 米棋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.82,0:20:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是夫婦這件事，\N我們不知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.39,0:21:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在大家知道啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.52,0:21:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我爸爸…  媽媽\N在哪裡呀！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.29,0:21:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以告訴我吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.43,0:21:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是胡索的媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.03,0:21:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,製造這部機動戰士的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.27,0:21:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,估不到啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.93,0:21:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你媽媽應該在月球的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.80,0:21:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷加 . 美利迪亞工場附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.30,0:21:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你爸爸的事就不知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.41,0:21:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為甚麽！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.04,0:21:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為他在策劃作戰部署
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.81,0:21:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,立即是那樣了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.51,0:21:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戰爭比任何事也重要吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.58,0:21:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了， 我們\N會公開V高達的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.52,0:21:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,機師中有胡索 . 艾賓這個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.42,0:21:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麽， 你父母就會和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.32,0:21:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連賀斯Jr聯絡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.09,0:21:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們以前沒那樣做嗎！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.33,0:21:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名字不能公開啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.00,0:21:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為甚麽！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.50,0:21:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們在進行反抗運動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.37,0:21:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不公開名字比較好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.10,0:21:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.80,0:21:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且， 我雖然\N對稱為V高達的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.61,0:21:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,機械有點怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.88,0:21:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我看來會喜歡這個機械人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.61,0:21:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為它是連繫胡索你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.68,0:22:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和你媽媽的機械人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.65,0:22:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是把人和人連繫起來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.48,0:22:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,機動戰士， 我會喜歡啊

